-- U.K. Stocks Are Little Changed; Technology Shares Gain
-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 2012-06-20T07:22:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-20/u-k-stocks-are-little-changed-technology-shares-gain.html
U.K. stocks were little changed as
gains in technology and financial companies offset a decline in
utility shares.  The FTSE 100 Index slipped 4.29 points, or 0.1 percent, to
5,582.02 at 8:20 a.m. in  London . The gauge has rallied 4.9
percent so far this month.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
